<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>READIN 집중력 훈련</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #FFC0CB, #FFB6C1);
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
        }

        .login-container {
            background: white;
            padding: 40px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            box-shadow: 0 15px 35px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 400px;
        }

        .logo {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }

        .logo h1 {
            color: #FFC0CB;
            font-size: 2.5em;
            font-weight: bold;
            text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        .logo p {
            color: #666;
            margin-top: 10px;
            font-size: 14px;
        }

        .form-group {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        label {
            display: block;
            margin-bottom: 8px;
            color: #333;
            font-weight: bold;
        }

        input[type="text"],
        input[type="password"] {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 12px;
            border: 2px solid #FFC0CB;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-size: 16px;
            transition: border-color 0.3s;
        }

        input[type="text"]:focus,
        input[type="password"]:focus {
            outline: none;
            border-color: #FF69B4;
        }

        .login-btn {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 12px;
            background: #FFC0CB;
            color: white;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 8px;
            font-size: 16px;
            font-weight: bold;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: background 0.3s;
        }

        .login-btn:hover {
            background: #FF69B4;
        }

        .error {
            background: #ffe6e6;
            color: #d63031;
            padding: 10px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .info {
            background: #e6f3ff;
            color: #0066cc;
            padding: 10px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 14px;
        }

        .auto-signup-info {
            margin-top: 20px;
            padding: 15px;
            background: #f0f8ff;
            border-radius: 8px;
            border-left: 4px solid #FFC0CB;
        }

        .auto-signup-info h3 {
            color: #FFC0CB;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .auto-signup-info p {
            color: #666;
            font-size: 14px;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="login-container">
        <div class="logo">
            <h1>READIN</h1>
            <p>독서논술코칭 방이센터 집중력 훈련</p>
        </div>

        <% if (error) { %>
        <div class="error">
            <%= error %>
        </div>
        <% } %>

        <form method="POST" action="/login">
            <div class="form-group">
                <label for="username">사용자 이름</label>
                <input type="text" id="username" name="username" required>
            </div>

            <div class="form-group">
                <label for="password">비밀번호</label>
                <input type="password" id="password" name="password" required>
            </div>

            <button type="submit" class="login-btn">로그인</button>
        </form>

        <% if (autoSignup) { %>
        <div class="auto-signup-info">
            <h3>신규 학생 안내</h3>
            <p>
                처음 참여하는 학생은 원하는 사용자 이름과 비밀번호 <strong>123456</strong>을 입력하면 
                자동으로 계정이 생성됩니다.
            </p>
        </div>
        <% } %>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
